I just came to this conclusion that only hate mongers on both side of borders are the politicians and the news channels.
If you don't believe me search for how Atif was insulted by media reporters in MTV interview.
But the beautiful part was many Indians were apologizing in the comments section on the behalf of those stupid journalists. People are not bad in India only their and our perception is bad about each other. But now slowly slowly I can sense the hatred and borders fading away. Love and respect to people of both countries who are opening their minds and hearts for each other.
